! Solarized Dark
*foreground:        #839496
*background:        #002b36
*.foreground:       #839496
*.background:       #002b36
emacs*foreground:   #839496
emacs*background:   #002b36
URxvt*foreground:   #839496
XTerm*foreground:   #839496
UXTerm*foreground:  #839496
URxvt*background:   [100]#002b36
XTerm*background:   #002b36
UXTerm*background:  #002b36
URxvt*cursorColor:  #93a1a1
XTerm*cursorColor:  #93a1a1
UXTerm*cursorColor: #93a1a1
URxvt*borderColor:  [100]#002b36

! Colors 0-15.
*.color0:  #073642
*color0:   #073642
